name: Bob Phillip
description:
I am an honest, kind, caring understand and of good sense of humor, passionate heart that’s looking for a stable relationship. I understand it is important to lay down lasting foundations for a lasting relationship. I am an active person who enjoys cycling and running best. I believe keeping fit is important. I am not interested in games or drama.
I am looking for a woman for living a great love, a long term relation, full of respect, love, tenderness, affection, devotion, loyalty. I am dame serious and wish a normal respectful life. I am romantic, intelligent, honest, loyal, who likes dinner with candles lights, wine, flowers, sports. I have a passionate temperament, maybe because I am so much romantic. When I love someone, love with my heart, soul and body. I believe God will send me the woman of my dreams: trustful, honored, gentle, patient, tolerant, no arrogant, generous on his gestures and actions. Someone for making me happy. Someone who I make happy and share with me the excellent and worse moments, because life is not only good things.So i live life to the fullest.
